slib_lang_exists_tmp=yes

slib_title=Probability density function of a Pascal law

slib_out=Values at <span class="tt">data</span> of the probability density function of the binomial law with parameters\
<span class="tt">n</span> and <span class="tt">p</span> (n is an integer and (0&lt;p&lt;1)).
slib_comment=<span class="tt">data</span> can be a list of integers.\
Probability density function of the total number of trials needed to get <span class="tt">n</span> successes \
if in each trial the probability of success is <span class="tt">p</span>.

